{"tid":1898421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"央視前主播促華向世界道歉","createTime":"2020-02-26T05:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T06:16:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb12d0165f4e22a38b6fe35be54d98f1877ce10","tid":1898421,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200226/ROXUFJXDIGM4VZDR6S66YO7KOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200226%2FROXUFJXDIGM4VZDR6S66YO7KOI%2F&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=d1d993ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200226%2FROXUFJXDIGM4VZDR6S66YO7KOI%2F&h=a0a9f84f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200226/ROXUFJXDIGM4VZDR6S66YO7KOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n央視前主播促華向世界道歉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200226/large/1582645973_277b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200226%2Flarge%2F1582645973_277b.gif&h=4bfa7b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邱孟煌<br />\n<br />\n中國驅逐三名《華爾街日報》記者的中美風波持續發酵，央視前主持人邱孟煌（阿丘）要求中國道歉，隨即受內地網民圍攻。內地網民認為，阿丘提出中國應向全世界道歉的言論「甚麼狗屁邏輯」，有網民反駁「武漢以封城的形式替全人類扛了，中國替全人類扛了」，指阿丘為潛在的排華行為提供道德依據──「中國人錯了，中國人該死」。<br />\n<br />\n邱孟煌上周四在微博留言：「雖然東亞病夫的牌匾早已踢碎了一個多世紀了，但我們可不可以說話語調稍溫和並帶些歉意，不慫也不豪橫（恃勢凌人）地把口罩戴起來，向世界鞠個躬，說聲：對不起，給你們添亂了。」阿丘的留言主要是回應美國《華爾街日報》題為《中國是真正的亞洲病夫》一文觸發的涉辱華風波。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受內地網民圍攻<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：緊急限制口罩出口 文在寅擬封鎖大邱<br />\n<br />\n據悉，丘已刪除相關微博留言，但網民對他的批評昨持續發酵：「奴才就是奴才，你叫他站起來他還不樂意。」「大褲衩（央視大總部的外號）出來的還真是個個妖魔鬼怪。」<br />\n<br />\n微博"},{"pid":"adaeb3ecace9fad8d4a4dafc138a5bcb27eb04e1","tid":1898421,"uid":54528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:38:28.000Z","msg":"中國係世界病夫, 仲要係超級帶菌人"},{"pid":"941777cf7262cf346ff28cfbee588f9489862934","tid":1898421,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />石堅認錯"},{"pid":"7c97fef3cc1cfe2685911d6ebbdfdb722eac25e7","tid":1898421,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"武漢以封城的形式替全人類扛了，中國替全人類扛了<br />\n<br />\n打飛機打出血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd66d11f88f7ba49ed600d00443cb3dd7b3a3f0c","tid":1898421,"uid":18177,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"根據因果關係，係因為中國武漢散播病毒，<br />\n<br />\n佢哋先要封城隔離，依家仲要傳到成個世界都係，<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔應該道歉？仲要封佢哋做英雄？<br />\n<br />\n痴9線國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a6b191e844187696e38c6d5c553137a725641c","tid":1898421,"uid":53446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"過兩日就會見到前主播係微博向中央道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62252155011b697edeadeef59a2f595d6add79a8","tid":1898421,"uid":235527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:54:34.000Z","msg":"「奴才就是奴才，你叫他站起來他還不樂意。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff453b6595c0475422140e4f92a8a685be12cff","tid":1898421,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWfaetG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWfaetG.jpg&h=eadfcec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea4a288fbfcd843167080936ae92b33687fc4fc2","tid":1898421,"uid":89517,"